Visor is a powerful Python library designed for efficient management and processing of large image datasets. It provides a streamlined solution for handling image data along with associated metadata and OCR information.

## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Efficient storage of image data, metadata, and OCR information
- âœ… Customizable image resizing options
- âœ… Fast reading and writing of large datasets
- âœ… Built-in data validation and error handling
- âœ… Easy-to-use API for dataset manipulation
- âœ… Support for compressed storage (optional)

